{"actor":"mistakeknot","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-11T18:38:06Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":62,"issue_id":"Lowbeer-2lf","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"Lowbeer-2lf\",\"title\":\"Research: macOS energy measurement APIs (IOReport, IOPSCopyPowerSourcesInfo, CPU proxy)\",\"description\":\"Research the available approaches for measuring per-process and system-level energy consumption on macOS/Apple Silicon. Compare: (1) CPU% * power coefficient proxy, (2) IOReport per-cluster power telemetry (private API, used by powermetrics), (3) IOPSCopyPowerSourcesInfo for system discharge rate. Determine which approach gives the best accuracy-to-complexity tradeoff for Lowbeer. Deliverable: brainstorm doc with API availability, code samples, accuracy assessment, and recommendation.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":0,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"mistakeknot@vibeguider.org\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-12T01:37:57Z\",\"created_by\":\"mistakeknot\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-12T01:37:57Z\"}"}
