{"actor":"mistakeknot","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-11T18:41:16Z","event_type":"updated","id":64,"issue_id":"Lowbeer-dni","new_value":"{\"description\":\"Subsumed by Lowbeer-waw (Battery Detective epic). The offender leaderboard is now a component of the integrated battery detective view — top energy offenders ranked by estimated Wh, with throttle actions.\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"Lowbeer-dni\",\"title\":\"Process offender leaderboard in popover\",\"description\":\"Show which processes/apps have consumed the most CPU over time (e.g., 'Claude Code: 45% of CPU this week'). Track cumulative CPU time per app identity.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"feature\",\"owner\":\"mistakeknot@vibeguider.org\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-10T02:41:47Z\",\"created_by\":\"350b45c0\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-10T02:41:47Z\"}"}
{"actor":"mistakeknot","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-11T18:41:17Z","event_type":"updated","id":65,"issue_id":"Lowbeer-squ","new_value":"{\"description\":\"Subsumed by Lowbeer-waw (Battery Detective epic). Battery savings counter is now part of the menu bar energy indicator and the detective view's daily savings summary.\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"Lowbeer-squ\",\"title\":\"Battery savings counter in menu bar\",\"description\":\"Show daily battery savings estimate in the menu bar (e.g., 'Saved 2.3h today'). Use CPU reduction * power coefficient model. Public API IOPSCopyPowerSourcesInfo for battery state.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"feature\",\"owner\":\"mistakeknot@vibeguider.org\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-10T02:41:45Z\",\"created_by\":\"350b45c0\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-10T02:41:45Z\"}"}
