{"actor":"mistakeknot","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-11T20:56:09Z","event_type":"status_changed","id":71,"issue_id":"Lowbeer-4ue","new_value":"{\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"Lowbeer-4ue\",\"title\":\"IOReport Swift bindings with graceful fallback\",\"description\":\"Wrap Apple Silicon IOReport private API in a clean Swift interface. Subscribe to Energy Model channels, sample at poll interval, return per-cluster power (P-core watts, E-core watts, GPU watts, total system watts). Graceful fallback to CPU% proxy if IOReport unavailable (older macOS, Intel, or API breakage). Reference implementations: socpowerbud (Obj-C), NeoAsitop (Swift), macmon (Rust).\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":0,\"issue_type\":\"task\",\"owner\":\"mistakeknot@vibeguider.org\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-12T03:55:37Z\",\"created_by\":\"mistakeknot\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-12T03:55:37Z\"}"}
